webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Sami people off the hut. A man, a woman and two young boys wearing Sami suits. The picture also shows a dog. “Lappans in the village of Jukkasjärvi.”(original text behind the picture). Postcard picture with the text “Lappar.” at the bottom left and “Fotograph 67/1 Axel Eliassons Konstförlag, Stockholm” at the bottom right - https://www.europeana.eu/item/2021008/_knp_137715.
